Schultz was forced
to step down when that news came
to light

03:52.766 --> 03:55.335 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
on the eve of the party
convention.

03:55.368 --> 03:58.839 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
