information to?

04:02.509 --> 04:03.477 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
I don't know.

04:03.510 --> 04:04.478 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Who dumped it?

04:04.511 --> 04:05.846 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
